snippet.title: AQUAMAN Movie Review (2018)
snippet.description:
JoBlo.com reviews the hugely-anticipated Warner Bros./DC superhero original film AQUAMAN starring Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Nicole Kidman and Patrick Wilson!

AQUAMAN is the movie by James Wan.

RELEASE DATE: 21 December 2018 (USA)
GENRE: Action, Adventure, Fantasy 
STARS: Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Willem Dafoe
